gameConfig.startingMemo: Emergency SOS beacon received. Origin point has been triangulated to planet Tallon IV in system FS-176. Navigation systems aligned to coordinates. Source of trasnmission unknown. Exercise caution.

artifactHints.Artifact of Chozo: The last hope of the &push;&main-color=#f76007;Chozo&pop; was gathered in our hour of peril and &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;planted as a seed&pop;, so that it may take form and cast shade from the sun in a great &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;plaza&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Nature: &push;&main-color=#f76007;Nature&pop; is said to reclaim us all in time, even in spirit. Our bretheren shall uphold this idea, even in death, where the &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;sun&pop; shines eternal.
artifactHints.Artifact of Sun: The &push;&main-color=#f76007;Sun&pop; brings &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;light&pop; and life to us all. May this Artifact feel it on all sides atop our highest &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;tower&pop; past a shrine in our home.
artifactHints.Artifact of World: The Newborn had a fascination with a man who held the whole &push;&main-color=#f76007;World&pop; in his &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;hands&pop; during her youth. In hopes of rekindling this nostalgia, those hands have been encased in &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;ice&pop; to cherish it.
artifactHints.Artifact of Spirit: A &push;&main-color=#f76007;Spirit&pop; true to itself cannot be weighed down. Let your spirit too become &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;weightless&pop; and rise to the top of this frigid &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;tower&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Newborn: During her adolescence, the ;&main-color=#f76007;Newborn&pop; had an obsession with riding a wooden board on wheels. We Chozo were never quite able to master the art of riding this contraption, but we encouraged her to &push;&main-color=#FF0000;shred&pop; to her heart's content and seek thrill in this frozen &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;canyon&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Truth: The &push;&main-color=#f76007;Truth&pop; is often hard to swallow, and even we in all our wisdom believe this to be true. Though, in this case, only a &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;swallow&pop; could rise to try in this flooded &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;pit&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Strength: The clumsy invaders believe only in &push;&main-color=#f76007;Strength&pop; and the pursuit of it. By their creed, if only the &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;strongest among them&pop; can survive, then let his power be tested in his own &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;quarters&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Elder: Our kind has held our &push;&main-color=#f76007;Elders&pop; in the highest respect for ages past. Above all else, their &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;security&pop; remains paramount to Chozo far and wide.
artifactHints.Artifact of Wild: Once the call of the &push;&main-color=#f76007;Wild&pop; has been heard, it is difficult to resist. Our departure from Elysia surely proves this, and our joy in peace on Tallon IV has been left near the site of a &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;great tree&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Lifegiver: The &push;&main-color=#f76007;Lifegiver&pop; among us is one who seeks to protect those in need. In the depths of our homeland is their purpose made true, hidden away in an industrious &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;depot&pop;.
artifactHints.Artifact of Warrior: The &push;&main-color=#f76007;Warrior&pop; within us all has been quiet for ages now. Yet our memory of times past lives on, honored in a &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;shrine&pop; in the caverns of Tallon.

extraScans.text: The heart of the vicious &push;&main-color=#f76007;seed&pop; that ravaged our home lies beyond. We pray for the &push;&main-color=#3BEC94;Newborn&pop; to return and protect our legacy here on Tallon.
